## Dart 3.4+ Dil Ozellikleri
```dart
// Sealed class + pattern matching (exhaustive switch)
sealed class Result<T> {}
final class Success<T> extends Result<T> { final T data; Success(this.data); }
final class Failure<T> extends Result<T> { final String message; Failure(this.message); }

String describe(Result<int> r) => switch (r) {
  Success(data: var d) => 'OK: $d',
  Failure(message: var m) => 'Hata: $m',
};
// Extension type — zero-cost wrapper
extension type UserId(String value) { bool get isValid => value.isNotEmpty && value.length <= 36; }
```
```
Class modifiers:
  base class -> Sadece extend; implement YASAK  |  final class -> Ne extend ne implement
  interface class -> Sadece implement; extend YASAK  |  sealed class -> Ayni kutuphane; exhaustiveness
```

