## State Management — Riverpod 2.0
```
Provider              -> Sabit deger, service instance
StateProvider         -> Basit degisken (filtre, toggle)
FutureProvider        -> Tek seferlik async veri
StreamProvider        -> Gercek zamanli veri (WebSocket)
AsyncNotifierProvider -> Async karmasik state (CRUD — onerilen)
Secim: Kucuk-orta proje -> Riverpod | Buyuk takim, strict event-driven -> BLoC
```
```dart
@riverpod
class ItemList extends _$ItemList {
  @override
  Future<List<Item>> build() => ref.read(itemRepositoryProvider).getAll();
  Future<void> addItem(CreateItemDto dto) async {
    state = const AsyncLoading();
    state = await AsyncValue.guard(() => ref.read(itemRepositoryProvider).create(dto));
  }
}
// Widget: ref.watch(itemListProvider).when(data: ..., loading: ..., error: ...)
```

## Navigation — GoRouter
```dart
final routerProvider = Provider<GoRouter>((ref) {
  final auth = ref.watch(authNotifierProvider);
  return GoRouter(
    refreshListenable: auth,
    redirect: (ctx, state) {
      if (!auth.isAuthenticated && state.matchedLocation != '/login') return '/login';
      if (auth.isAuthenticated && state.matchedLocation == '/login') return '/home';
      return null;
    },
    routes: [
      ShellRoute(builder: (_, __, child) => AppShell(child: child), routes: [
        GoRoute(path: '/home', builder: (_, __) => const HomePage()),
        GoRoute(path: '/items/:id', builder: (_, s) => ItemDetailPage(id: s.pathParameters['id']!)),
      ]),
      GoRoute(path: '/login', builder: (_, __) => const LoginPage()),
    ],
  );
});
```

## Networking — dio + Hata Yonetimi
```dart
@riverpod
Dio dio(Ref ref) => Dio(BaseOptions(
  baseUrl: const String.fromEnvironment('API_BASE_URL'),
  connectTimeout: const Duration(seconds: 10), receiveTimeout: const Duration(seconds: 15),
))..interceptors.addAll([AuthInterceptor(ref), LogInterceptor(requestBody: true, responseBody: true)]);

sealed class AppFailure { final String message; const AppFailure(this.message); }
final class NetworkFailure extends AppFailure { const NetworkFailure(super.message); }
final class ServerFailure extends AppFailure { const ServerFailure(super.message); }
final class ValidationFailure extends AppFailure {
  final Map<String, List<String>> fieldErrors;
  const ValidationFailure(super.message, this.fieldErrors);
}
```

