## Naming Conventions (Dart)
```
Dosya -> snake_case (item_detail_page.dart)  |  Class/enum -> UpperCamelCase (ItemDetailPage)
Degisken -> lowerCamelCase (itemCount)       |  Private -> _prefix (_internalState)
Sabit -> lowerCamelCase (maxRetryCount)      |  Boolean -> is/has/can/should (isLoading, hasData)
```

## Anti-Pattern'ler
| Anti-Pattern | Dogru Yaklasim |
|---|---|
| `setState` icinde agir is mantigi | Riverpod/BLoC ile state ayir; widget sadece gosterim |
| Fat widget (build 200+ satir) | Kucuk, tek sorumluluklu widget'lara bol |
| `.map()` icinde key eksikligi | `ValueKey` veya benzersiz key ver |
| BoxConstraints ihmal etme | LayoutBuilder / ConstrainedBox ile responsive tasarim |
| BuildContext async gap sonrasi | `if (!mounted) return;` kontrolu veya ref kullan |
| `print()` ile debug | `debugPrint()` veya logger; production'da log seviyesi |
| God-class repository | Feature bazli repository + use case katmani |
| Hardcoded string UI'da | `flutter_localizations` + ARB dosyalari ile i18n |
| Her widget'ta `FutureBuilder` | Riverpod AsyncNotifier veya FutureProvider |
| `Platform.isAndroid` widget'ta | `defaultTargetPlatform` veya `Theme.of(context).platform` |
| Tum state global provider | Sayfa bazli / scoped provider; gereksiz rebuild onle |
| Image olceklendirmeden | `cached_network_image` + cacheWidth/cacheHeight |

## Performans
```
DevTools: Widget rebuild tracker | Timeline (jank) | Memory (leak) | Network profiler
├── const constructor      -> Widget rebuild azalt (MUMKUNSE const)
├── RepaintBoundary        -> Agir animasyon izolasyonu
├── ListView.builder       -> Lazy rendering (ASLA ListView(children:[]) degil)
├── cacheWidth/cacheHeight -> Image bellekte boyut siniri
├── Isolate.run            -> CPU-yogun is ana thread'den ayir
├── --split-debug-info     -> Release build boyutunu kucult
